  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">
      Given a valid entity pair, when GET profiles/{source}/{target} is called, then the profile
      with all rules is returned with HTTP 200.
    </criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">
      Given an invalid entity pair, when GET profiles/{source}/{target} is called, then HTTP 404
      with ProblemDetails is returned.
    </criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Integration tests pass.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Response should include rules array:
    - rules: [{ id, sourceField, targetField, sourceType, targetType, isReversible }]

    This endpoint is performance-critical as it's called during record selection in PCF.
  </notes>

